<subSubSection id="771FACDA96FD3A17E55B5A5BBD793F8C" pageId="0" pageNumber="595" type="distribution">
<paragraph id="0F435590DD9E7B0F800EDCC8DE5C8155" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">Local distribution and ecology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AD46F7F9CD831DB840B698DC4B2A9335" pageId="0" pageNumber="595">This species was (and is) distributed over the dry steppes in the south-western part of the region. Its rare populations are associated with the very dry steppe habitats. Its populations may be abundant in the semi-deserts and north deserts of Kazakhstan.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
